rows.label: fev01_130_125_msg0001
rows.name:
We won't reach the uncharted area until
tomorrow... Still a long way to go.

rows.label: fev01_130_125_msg0002
rows.name: For now, should I go talk to the clients?

rows.label: fev01_130_125_msg0003
rows.name:
I'd like to learn more about
who they are...

rows.label: fev01_130_125_msg0004
rows.name:
It's not like I get to chat with Drivers
every day, after all.

rows.label: fev01_130_125_msg0005
rows.name:
Afterward, I should head
over to see Monell.

rows.label: fev01_130_125_msg0006
rows.name:
I promised to take the night watch,
and he'll be upset if I don't show up.
